Step.SQLStatement: CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW am_asset_meter_log_v AS SELECT aml.datetrx AS log_datetrx, aml.description AS log_description, aml.amt AS log_measured_amt, aml.currentamt AS log_total_amt, am.value AS assetmetervalue, am.name AS assetmetername, am.amt AS assetmeteramt, a.value AS assetvalue, a.name AS assetname, mt.name AS mtname, aml.ad_client_id, aml.ad_org_id, aml.ad_user_id, am.am_assetmeter_id, a.a_asset_id, mt.am_meter_id FROM am_assetmeter_log aml JOIN am_assetmeter am ON aml.am_assetmeter_id = am.am_assetmeter_id JOIN a_asset a ON am.a_asset_id = a.a_asset_id JOIN am_meter mt ON am.am_meter_id = mt.am_meter_id;

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW am_asset_meters_v AS SELECT a.value AS assetvalue, a.name AS assetname, am.value AS assetmetervalue, am.name AS assetmetername, am.amt AS assetmeteramt, mt.name AS metername, ( SELECT max(aml.datetrx) AS max FROM am_assetmeter_log aml WHERE aml.am_assetmeter_id = am.am_assetmeter_id) AS lastlogdate, am.datetrx AS am_datetrx, a.ad_client_id, a.ad_org_id, a.a_asset_id, a.a_asset_group_id, am.am_assetmeter_id FROM a_asset a JOIN am_assetmeter am ON a.a_asset_id = am.a_asset_id JOIN am_meter mt ON am.am_meter_id = mt.am_meter_id WHERE a.isactive = 'Y'::bpchar AND am.isactive = 'Y'::bpchar;

mp.datelastso AS mp_datelastot, mp.costamt AS mp_costamt, mp.maintenancearea AS mp_maintainarea_short, mp.am_calendartype, refl2.name AS mp_maintain_area_long, ( SELECT rl.name FROM ad_ref_list rl WHERE rl.ad_reference_id = 154::numeric AND rl.value::bpchar = mp.priorityrule) AS mp_priority, ( SELECT rl.name FROM ad_ref_list rl WHERE rl.ad_reference_id = 53827::numeric AND rl.value::bpchar = mp.am_programmingtype) AS mp_manttype, ( SELECT rl.name FROM ad_ref_list rl WHERE rl.ad_reference_id = 53822::numeric AND rl.value::text = mp.docstatus::text) AS mp_status, a.value AS mp_assetvalue, a.name AS mp_assetname, ag.name AS mp_assetgroupname, jb.name AS mp_stdjob, t.line AS task_line, t.name AS task_name, t.description AS task_jobdescription, t.costamt AS task_costamt, r.resourcetype AS resource_type_short, refl1.name AS resource_type_long, r.resourceqty AS resource_qty, prd.value AS resource_prdvalue, prd.name AS resource_prdname, rsc.value AS resource_value, rsc.name AS resource_name, r.costamt AS resource_cost, uom.name AS resource_uom, mp.ad_client_id, mp.ad_org_id, mp.am_maintenance_id, t.am_maintenance_task_id, r.am_maintenance_resource_id, a.a_asset_id, ag.a_asset_group_id, jb.am_maintenancepattern_id, uom.c_uom_id, prd.m_product_id, rsc.s_resource_id FROM am_maintenance mp LEFT JOIN a_asset a ON mp.a_asset_id = a.a_asset_id LEFT JOIN a_asset_group ag ON mp.a_asset_group_id = ag.a_asset_group_id LEFT JOIN am_maintenancepattern jb ON mp.am_maintenancepattern_id = jb.am_maintenancepattern_id LEFT JOIN ad_ref_list refl2 ON refl2.ad_reference_id = 53818::numeric AND mp.maintenancearea::text = refl2.value::text LEFT JOIN am_maintenance_task t ON mp.am_maintenance_id = t.am_maintenance_id LEFT JOIN am_maintenance_resource r ON t.am_maintenance_task_id = r.am_maintenance_task_id LEFT JOIN m_product prd ON r.m_product_id = prd.m_product_id LEFT JOIN s_resource rsc ON r.s_resource_id = rsc.s_resource_id LEFT JOIN c_uom uom ON r.c_uom_id = uom.c_uom_id LEFT JOIN ad_ref_list refl1 ON refl1.ad_reference_id = 53821::numeric AND r.resourcetype::text = refl1.value::text WHERE mp.am_programmingtype = 'C'::bpchar;

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW am_maintenance_meter_v AS SELECT mt.name AS mp_metername, mt.isactive AS mp_active, mp.costamt AS mp_costamt, mp.maintenancearea AS mp_maintainarea_short, refl2.name AS t.isactive AS task_active, t.costamt AS task_costamt, r.resourcetype AS resource_type_short, refl1.name AS resource_type_long, r.resourceqty AS resource_qty, r.isactive AS resource_active, prd.value AS resource_prdvalue, prd.name AS resource_prdname, rsc.value AS resource_value, rsc.name AS resource_name, r.costamt AS resource_cost, uom.name AS resource_uom, mp.ad_client_id, mp.ad_org_id, rsc.s_resource_id FROM am_maintenance mp LEFT JOIN am_meter mt ON mp.am_meter_id = mt.am_meter_id LEFT JOIN a_asset a ON mp.a_asset_id = a.a_asset_id LEFT JOIN a_asset_group ag ON mp.a_asset_group_id = ag.a_asset_group_id LEFT JOIN am_maintenancepattern jb ON mp.am_maintenancepattern_id = jb.am_maintenancepattern_id LEFT JOIN ad_ref_list refl2 ON refl2.ad_reference_id = 53818::numeric AND mp.maintenancearea::text = refl2.value::text LEFT JOIN am_maintenance_task t ON mp.am_maintenance_id = t.am_maintenance_id LEFT JOIN am_maintenance_resource r ON t.am_maintenance_task_id = r.am_maintenance_task_id LEFT JOIN m_product prd ON r.m_product_id = prd.m_product_id LEFT JOIN s_resource rsc ON r.s_resource_id = rsc.s_resource_id LEFT JOIN c_uom uom ON r.c_uom_id = uom.c_uom_id CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW am_maintenance_v AS SELECT mp.documentno AS mp_documentno, mp."interval" AS mp_interval, mp.datelastrun AS mp_datelastrun, mp.datenextrun AS mp_datenextrun, mp.datelastso AS mp_datelastot, mp.costamt AS mp_costamt, mp.maintenancearea AS mp_maintainarea_short, mp.am_calendartype, refl2.name AS mp_maintain_area_long, refl3.description AS mp_calendartype_long, ( SELECT rl.name FROM ad_ref_list rl WHERE rl.ad_reference_id = 154::numeric AND rl.value::bpchar = mp.priorityrule) AS mp_priority, ( SELECT rl.name FROM ad_ref_list rl WHERE rl.ad_reference_id = 53827::numeric AND rl.value::bpchar = mp.am_programmingtype) AS mp_manttype, ( SELECT rl.value FROM ad_ref_list rl WHERE rl.ad_reference_id = 53827::numeric AND rl.value::bpchar = mp.am_programmingtype) AS mp_manttypeshort, ( SELECT rl.name FROM ad_ref_list rl WHERE rl.ad_reference_id = 23822::numeric AND rl.value::text = mp.docstatus::text) AS mp_status, a.value AS mp_assetvalue, a.name AS mp_assetname, ag.name AS mp_assetgroupname, jb.name AS mp_stdjob, mp.isactive, usr.name AS username, usr.value AS uservalue, mp.ad_client_id, mp.ad_org_id, mp.am_maintenance_id, a.a_asset_id, ag.a_asset_group_id, jb.am_maintenancepattern_id, usr.ad_user_id FROM am_maintenance mp LEFT JOIN a_asset a ON mp.a_asset_id = a.a_asset_id LEFT JOIN a_asset_group ag ON mp.a_asset_group_id = ag.a_asset_group_id LEFT JOIN am_maintenancepattern jb ON mp.am_maintenancepattern_id = jb.am_maintenancepattern_id LEFT JOIN ad_ref_list refl2 ON refl2.ad_reference_id = 53818::numeric AND mp.maintenancearea::text = refl2.value::text LEFT JOIN ad_ref_list refl3 ON refl3.ad_reference_id = 83823::numeric AND mp.am_calendartype::text = refl3.value::text LEFT JOIN ad_user usr ON mp.ad_user_id = usr.ad_user_id WHERE mp.am_programmingtype = 'C'::bpchar;

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW am_maintenancepattern_v AS SELECT jb.name AS sj_jobname, jb.costamt AS sj_costamt, jb.maintenancearea AS sj_maintainarea_short, refl.name AS sj_maintain_area_long, a.value AS sj_assetvalue, a.name AS sj_assetname, ag.name AS sj_assetgroupname, t.line AS task_line, t.name AS task_name, t.description AS task_jobdescription, t.costamt AS task_cost, r.resourcetype AS resource_type_short, refl1.name AS resource_type_long, r.resourceqty AS resource_qty, prd.value AS resource_prdvalue, prd.name AS resource_prdname, rsc.value AS resource_value, rsc.name AS resource_name, r.costamt AS resource_cost, uom.name AS resource_uom, jb.ad_client_id, jb.ad_org_id, jb.am_maintenancepattern_id, t.am_maintenancepattern_task_id, r.am_maintpattern_resource_id, a.a_asset_id, ag.a_asset_group_id, uom.c_uom_id, prd.m_product_id, rsc.s_resource_id FROM am_maintenancepattern jb LEFT JOIN a_asset a ON jb.a_asset_id = a.a_asset_id LEFT JOIN a_asset_group ag ON jb.a_asset_group_id = ag.a_asset_group_id LEFT JOIN ad_ref_list refl ON refl.ad_reference_id = 53818::numeric AND jb.maintenancearea::text = refl.value::text LEFT JOIN am_maintenancepattern_task t ON jb.am_maintenancepattern_id = t.am_maintenancepattern_id LEFT JOIN am_maintpattern_resource r ON t.am_maintenancepattern_task_id = r.am_maintenancepattern_task_id LEFT JOIN m_product prd ON r.m_product_id = prd.m_product_id LEFT JOIN s_resource rsc ON r.s_resource_id = rsc.s_resource_id LEFT JOIN c_uom uom ON r.c_uom_id = uom.c_uom_id LEFT JOIN ad_ref_list refl1 ON refl1.ad_reference_id = 53821::numeric AND r.resourcetype::text = refl1.value::text;

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW am_serviceorder_v AS SELECT ot.documentno AS ot_documentno, ot.datetrx AS ot_datetrx, ot.datestartplan AS ot_datestartplan, ot.datefinish AS ot_datefinish, ot.processed AS ot_processed, ot.description AS ot_description, ot.isactive AS ot_active, ot.costamt AS ot_costamt, ot.costamtplan AS ot_costplan, ot.maintenancearea AS ot_maintainarea_short, refl2.name AS ot_maintain_area_long, ( SELECT rl.name FROM ad_ref_list rl WHERE rl.ad_reference_id = 131::numeric AND rl.value::text = ot.docstatus::text) AS ot_status_long, ot.docstatus AS ot_status_short, a.value AS ot_assetvalue, a.name AS ot_assetname, usr.name AS ot_usrname, wh.value AS ot_whvalue, wh.name AS ot_whname, mp.documentno AS ot_mpdocumentno, otr.documentno AS ot_otrequest_documentno, js.name AS ot_jobstandard, t.line AS task_line, t.name AS task_name, t.description AS task_description, t.processed AS task_tprocessed, t.isactive AS task_active, t.costamt AS task_costamt, t.costamtplan AS task_costamtplan, ( SELECT rl.name FROM ad_ref_list rl WHERE rl.ad_reference_id = 53833::numeric AND rl.value::text = t.status::text) AS task_status, r.resourcetype AS resource_type_short, refl1.name AS resource_type_long, r.resourceqty AS resource_qty, r.qtyplan AS resource_qtyplan, r.qtyreserved AS resource_qtyreserved, r.qtydelivered AS resource_qtydelivered, r.isactive AS resource_active, prd.value AS resource_prdvalue, prd.name AS resource_prdname, rsc.value AS resource_rscvalue, rsc.name AS resource_rscname, r.costamt AS resource_costamt, r.costamtplan AS resource_costamtplan, uom.name AS resource_uom, ot.ad_client_id, ot.ad_org_id, ot.am_serviceorder_id, r.am_serviceorder_task_id, r.am_serviceorder_resource_id, a.a_asset_id, a.a_asset_group_id, usr.ad_user_id, wh.m_warehouse_id, mp.am_maintenance_id, otr.am_serviceorder_request_id, js.am_maintenancepattern_id, uom.c_uom_id, prd.m_product_id, rsc.s_resource_id FROM am_serviceorder ot LEFT JOIN a_asset a ON ot.a_asset_id = a.a_asset_id LEFT JOIN ad_user usr ON ot.ad_user_id = usr.ad_user_id LEFT JOIN m_warehouse wh ON ot.m_warehouse_id = wh.m_warehouse_id LEFT JOIN am_maintenance mp ON ot.am_maintenance_id = mp.am_maintenance_id LEFT JOIN am_serviceorder_request otr ON ot.am_serviceorder_request_id = otr.am_serviceorder_request_id LEFT JOIN am_maintenancepattern js ON ot.am_maintenancepattern_id = js.am_maintenancepattern_id LEFT JOIN ad_ref_list refl2 ON refl2.ad_reference_id = 53818::numeric AND ot.maintenancearea::text = refl2.value::text LEFT JOIN am_serviceorder_task t ON ot.am_serviceorder_id = t.am_serviceorder_id LEFT JOIN am_serviceorder_resource r ON t.am_serviceorder_id = r.am_serviceorder_task_id LEFT JOIN m_product prd ON r.m_product_id = prd.m_product_id LEFT JOIN s_resource rsc ON r.s_resource_id = rsc.s_resource_id LEFT JOIN c_uom uom ON r.c_uom_id = uom.c_uom_id LEFT JOIN ad_ref_list refl1 ON refl1.ad_reference_id = 53821::numeric AND r.resourcetype::text = refl1.value::text;

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports. There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records: (1) The system requires the record for audit purposes. (2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.
The record is active in the system
The Created field indicates the date that this record was created.
The Updated field indicates the date that this record was updated.
The Created By field indicates the user who created this record.
The Updated By field indicates the user who updated this record.
